column13: Two model exams were conducted for this course which we felt difficult due to lack of time as we need to complete our record, take printouts, workout the codes etc. Meanwhile we were also need to concentrate on other subjects too.

Two model exams were conducted for this course which we felt difficult due to lack of time as we need to complete our record, take printouts, workout the codes etc. Meanwhile we were also need to concentrate on other subjects too. And the questions during model exams and terminal practical exams were of practical application and which were not taught/discussed during lecture hours even as an example
column15: Not satisfied with the model exams and terminal practical exams since concepts were in application type which were not discussed during lecture hours
